# Supply-chain cooldown (requires npm >= 11.10.0).
# Refuse to install package versions published fewer than this many DAYS ago,
# so the ecosystem has time to detect a malicious/compromised release before it
# can enter our dependency tree. Governs `npm install` and `npm update` at
# resolution time — including AI-agent-driven installs in this repo.
#
# Not enforced by `npm ci` (it installs the exact versions already pinned in
# package-lock.json) and ignored by npm < 11.10.0. Automated PRs get an
# equivalent cooldown via .github/dependabot.yml.
#
# Escape hatch for an URGENT security fix newer than the window (npm has no
# per-package exclusion yet): override per command, e.g.
#   npm install next@latest --min-release-age=0
min-release-age=7
